FIX 2 — RING TEXT "ASSOCIAT / E" STILL BREAKING
════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The word "Associate" does not fit in the inner circle.
The previous fix used white-space: nowrap but the
circle is too small to contain it at the current
font size. Two things need to change simultaneously.

In floating-persona-btn.component.scss:

### Make inner circle wider (it is a circle so
### width = height, but we can use a wider ellipse
### OR just increase the font size logic)

.inner-circle {
  width: 98px;
  height: 98px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0 8px;          /* horizontal padding */
  gap: 3px;
  overflow: hidden;        /* clip if still too long */
}

/* The label stack */
.persona-label-top {
  font-size: 0.44rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  white-space: nowrap;
  color: rgba(0, 200, 140, 0.55);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 1;
}

.persona-label-role {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;  /* Inter not Syne —
    Inter is narrower and fits better in small spaces */
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
  white-space: nowrap;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;  /* tight tracking */
  line-height: 1;
  display: block;
  max-width: none;
  overflow: visible;

  /* Dynamic font size based on name length:
     Short names (< 7 chars): 0.78rem
     Medium names (7-9 chars): 0.68rem  
     Long names (10+ chars): 0.58rem  */
  font-size: 0.78rem;
}

/* Apply size classes based on name length */
.persona-label-role.name-medium {
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.05em;
}

.persona-label-role.name-long {
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.06em;
}

### In floating-persona-btn.component.ts:

/* Replace isLongName getter with nameLength getter */

get nameLengthClass(): string {
  const name = this.currentPersona;
  if (name.length >= 10) return 'name-long';
  if (name.length >= 7)  return 'name-medium';
  return '';
}

/* Persona names and their expected classes:
   "Associate"  = 9 chars → name-medium → 0.68rem
   "Manager"    = 7 chars → name-medium → 0.68rem
   "HR Partner" = 10 chars → name-long  → 0.58rem */

### In floating-persona-btn.component.html:

<span class="persona-label-role"
  [class]="'persona-label-role ' + nameLengthClass">
  {{ currentPersona }}
</span>

