FIX 3 — "ASK CST" BUTTON REPOSITIONED
════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The Ask CST button is floating mid-page overlapping
journey chips. It should be fixed to the bottom of
the screen, not floating in the content area.

Find the Ask CST button in persona.component.html
or wherever it is rendered.

In its SCSS (or persona.component.scss):

/* If it has its own class — adjust selector */
.ask-cst-btn,
[class*="ask-cst"],
[class*="ask-btn"],
button:contains("Ask CST") {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 2rem;
  left: 2rem;            /* bottom LEFT — opposite side
                            from the persona ring button
                            which is bottom RIGHT */
  z-index: 9998;
  
  background: transparent;
  border: 1.5px solid #00C896;
  color: #00C896;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
